== 延伸阅读 ==
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20060908003557/http://www.rimric.com/folio/sp04/wiki.htm The Messiness of WikiDemocracy] - 出自 M.R.M. Parrott.
* [http://technology.guardian.co.uk/weekly/story/0,,1752257,00.html A thirst for knowledge] {{Wayback|url=http://technology.guardian.co.uk/weekly/story/0,,1752257,00.html |date=20080724205841 }} ''Guardian'' article 出自 Andrew Orlowski
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20060614203004/http://numenor.lib.uic.edu/fmconference/viewabstract.php?id=69 Trust And Wikipedia] - 一篇关于维基百科并指出其许多错误的研究论文。
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20060201230047/http://www.corante.com/many/archives/2004/08/29/wikipedia_reputation_and_the_wemedia_project.php Wikipedia Reputation and the Wemedia Project] - 出自 Ross Mayfield, 2004年8月29日.
* [http://www.kuro5hin.org/story/2004/12/30/142458/25 Why Wikipedia Must Jettison Its Anti-Elitism] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kuro5hin.org/story/2004/12/30/142458/25 |date=20060104040708 }} - 出自 Larry Sanger, co-founder of Wikipedia. 2004年12月30日.
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070221053253/http://slate.msn.com/id/2117942/ Wikipedia is a real-life Hitchhiker's Guide: huge, nerdy, and imprecise] - 出自 Paul Boutin, ''Slate'', 2005年5月3日.
* [http://www.cadenhead.org/workbench/news/2725/wikipedia-agony-delete Wikipedia: The Agony of Delete] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cadenhead.org/workbench/news/2725/wikipedia-agony-delete |date=20080703222251 }} - 出自 Rogers Cadenhead, 2005年8月31日.
* [http://www.guardian.co.uk/g2/story/0,,1599116,00.html Can you trust Wikipedia?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/g2/story/0,,1599116,00.html |date=20081008023529 }} - 出自 Mike Barnes, ''The Guardian'', 2005年10月24日.
* [http://www.theregister.com/2005/10/24/wikipedia_letters/ Wikipedia: magic, monkeys and typewriters] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theregister.com/2005/10/24/wikipedia_letters/ |date=20210308232406 }} - 出自 Andrew Orlowski, ''The Register'', 2005年10月24日.
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20160303195530/http://mg.co.za/articlePage.aspx?articleid=255920&area=%2Finsight%2Finsight__national%2F Can you trust Wikipedia?] - 出自 Elvira van Noort, ''Mail & Guardian'' (South Africa), 2005年11月7日.
* [http://www.usatoday.com/news/opinion/editorials/2005-11-29-wikipedia-edit_x.htm A false Wikipedia 'biography'] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/64PWOeCKO?url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/opinion/editorials/2005-11-29-wikipedia-edit_x.htm |date=20120103074618 |dateformat=iso }} - 出自 John Seigenthaler Sr., ''USA Today'', 2005年11月29日.
* [http://www.editorandpublisher.com/eandp/departments/online/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1001612397 "The Danger of Wikipedia"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.editorandpublisher.com/eandp/departments/online/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1001612397 |date=20100228161148 }}, ''Editor and Publisher'', 2005年11月30日. (需登入)
* [http://www.nytimes.com/2005/12/04/weekinreview/04seelye.html Snared in the Web of a Wikipedia Liar] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2005/12/04/weekinreview/04seelye.html |date=20140907013706 }} - 出自 Katharine Q. Seelye in [http://nytimes.com ''The New York Times''], 2005年12月3日.
* [http://www.timesonline.co.uk/article/0,,3284-1916781,00.html Unreliable (adj): log on and see] {{Wayback|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/article/0,,3284-1916781,00.html |date=20080703231108 }} - 出自 Rosemary Righter, ''The Times'', 2005年12月9日
* [http://www.theage.com.au/news/national/online-encyclopedias-put-to-the-test/2005/12/14/1134500913345.html Online encyclopedias put to the test] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/national/online-encyclopedias-put-to-the-test/2005/12/14/1134500913345.html |date=20180315175641 }} - 出自 Stephen Cauchi, 2005年12月14日.
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070927065033/http://www.theoneclickgroup.co.uk/news.php?start=1060&end=1080&view=yes&id=1155 Founded On Porn, Wikipedia Shapes The Way You Think] - 出自 Jennifer Monroe, 2005年12月15日.
* [http://www.theregister.co.uk/2005/12/16/wikipedia_britannica_science_comparison Wikipedia science 31% more cronky than Britannica's] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2005/12/16/wikipedia_britannica_science_comparison |date=20190620212204 }} - 出自 Andrew Orlowski, [http://www.theregister.co.uk ''The Register''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/ |date=20200529113716 }}, 2005年12月16日.
* [http://www.theregister.co.uk/2005/10/18/wikipedia_quality_problem/ "Wikipedia founder admits to serious quality problems"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2005/10/18/wikipedia_quality_problem/ |date=20200523054313 }} - 出自 Andrew Orlowski, ''The Register'', 2005年12月18日.
* [http://www.cadenhead.org/workbench/news/2828/wikipedia-founder-looks-out-number-1 Wikipedia Founder Looks Out for Number 1] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cadenhead.org/workbench/news/2828/wikipedia-founder-looks-out-number-1 |date=20080926103410 }} - 出自 Rogers Cadenhead, 2005年12月19日.
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20071013025750/http://dailycamera.com/bdc/buffzone_news/article/0,1713,BDC_2448_4444477,00.html Profs knock Wikipedia] - 出自 Brittany Anas, 2006年2月6日. （需登入）
* [http://www.neilgaiman.com/journal/2006/05/what-bears-do-on-lawn.html Neil Gaiman: What Bears Do On the Lawn] {{Wayback|url=http://www.neilgaiman.com/journal/2006/05/what-bears-do-on-lawn.html |date=20081204102737 }}, 2006年5月11日 - 作家和散文家[[尼尔·盖曼|尼尔·盖曼]]对维基百科的批评。
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20060718154001/http://www.boingboing.net/2006/05/22/u_florida_cops_ask_f.html "U. Florida cops ask fiction writer for fingerprints, DNA"], ''boingboing'', 2006年5月22日.

